mslRemarks: There is no waste water re-use in Estonia.
temporary storage on own platforms, treated sludge by other methods, compost
The 3115 t DS/y mentioned in others refers to the quantity of sludge temporarily stored on site, awaiting for the proper time to be reused in agriculture.

Sewage Sludge is disposed to the collection system (sewer network) of the ' Malta South' agglomeration. The Sant Antnin Urban Waste Water Treatment Plant is not equipped with a sludge thickening/dewatering line.
